window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>In this ninth novel in her acclaimed Young Wizards series, <i>New York Times</i> best-selling author Diane Duane whisks listeners away to Mars for a compelling adventure. </p> <p>While young wizards Kit and Nita investigate the mystery of the Red Planet’s long-lost inhabitants, life suddenly emerges again to shake Mars with its own perilous and baffling brand of magic. Kit’s long-standing Martian fascination ensnares him in a terrible, age-old conflict—making him a key to its solution or a tool for destroying humans. As Nita searches for Kit, she soon finds herself battling an implacable foe.</p>"; 
